{
  "name": "UniqueValues",
  "summary": "<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例通过条件格式规则生成一个动态数据集并对重复值应用颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Name&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Number&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Agent1&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFill</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2:A26&quot;</span>), xlFillDefault)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2:B26&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormulaArray</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=INT(RAND()*101)&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2:B26&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddUniqueValues</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DupeUnique</span> = xlDuplicate\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n    font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternColorIndex</span> = xlAutomatic\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作表上单元格区域 C1:C10 的第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式所应用于的单元格区域，并设置该条件格式内部唯一值的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C7:C10&quot;</span>))\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DupeUnique</span> = xlUnique\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p><strong>UniqueValues</strong> 对象使用 <strong>DupeUnique</strong> 属性返回或设置一个枚举，该枚举确定规则是查找区域中的重复值还是唯一值。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "<p>您可以将此属性与 OLE 自动化对象一起使用以返回该对象的应用程序。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果不与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象。如果与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表指定对象的创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "AppliesTo",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Range</strong> 对象，指定格式规则将应用于的单元格区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式应用到的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AppliesTo</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式应用到的单元格区域的地址赋值给 A1 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AppliesTo</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Borders",
      "summary": "<p>对于条件格式对象，您只能为单元格的上边框、下边框和侧边框设置属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Borders</strong> 集合，该集合在条件格式规则的计算结果为 <strong>True</strong> 时指定单元格边框的格式。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将工作表 Sheet1 中区域 C1:C10 的第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式的右边框设置为蓝色虚线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> boder = uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEdgeRight)\n    boder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlDash\n    boder.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个条件格式边框的线条样式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> boders = uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>\n    boders.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlDouble\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Borders",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DupeUnique",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong>XlDupeUnique</strong> 枚举的常量之一，指定条件格式规则是查找唯一的值还是查找重复的值。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式是否查找重复的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DupeUnique</span> == xlDuplicate)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式设置为查找唯一的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DupeUnique</span> = xlUnique\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlDupeUnique",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Font",
      "summary": "<p>条件格式对象并不支持 <strong>Font</strong> 对象的所有属性。您可以设置字体样式、下划线、颜色和删除线属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Font</strong> 对象，该对象在条件格式规则的计算结果为 <strong>True</strong> 时指定字体格式。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式的特定文本的字体的颜色和字号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">15</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式特定文本的字体设置为加粗和倾斜，并设置该字体的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Italic</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Font",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Interior",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Interior</strong> 对象，该对象在条件格式规则的计算结果为 <strong>True</strong> 时指定单元格的内部属性。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式内部的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">155</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式内部的主题颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent6\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Interior",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "NumberFormat",
      "summary": "<p>数字格式是使用**“单元格格式”<strong>对话框的</strong>“数字”**选项卡上显示的相同格式代码指定的。您可以使用内置的数字格式，例如 <code>&quot;General&quot;</code> 或者创建自定义数字格式。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>在条件格式规则的计算结果为 <strong>True</strong> 时返回或设置应用于单元格的数字格式。<strong>Variant</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式所应用于的数字格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NumberFormat</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式所应用于的数字格式，并设置该条件格式内部的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NumberFormat</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;0.00%&quot;</span>\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Priority",
      "summary": "<p>设置优先级时，值必须为介于 1 和工作表上条件格式规则总数之间的正整数。对于工作表上的所有规则，优先级必须为唯一值，因此，如果更改指定条件格式规则的优先级，将可能会导致工作表上其他规则的优先级值移位。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置条件格式规则的优先级值。当工作表中存在多个条件格式规则时，优先级确定求值的顺序。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 上区域 B1:B10 中第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "StopIfTrue",
      "summary": "<p>为了支持向后兼容性，此属性的默认值为 <strong>True</strong>，而这与在用户界面中创建的格式规则的行为相反。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，该值确定在当前规则的计算结果为 <strong>True</strong> 时是否应计算单元格上的其他格式规则。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断工作表 Sheet1 上区域 B1:B10 中第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式的计算结果为True时是否停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">StopIfTrue</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;条件格式的计算结果为 True 时停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;条件格式的计算结果为 True 时计算单元格上的其他格式规则&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式设置为当计算结果为True时停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">StopIfTrue</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "<p>此属性将始终返回 <strong>Long</strong> 值“8”，等价于 <strong>xlUniqueValues</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>XlFormatConditionType</strong> 枚举的常量之一，该常量指定条件格式的类型。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第二个条件格式的类型是否为xlUniqueValues。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> formatCondition = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(formatCondition.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlUniqueValues)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第一个条件格式的类型是否为xlUniqueValues，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> formatCondition = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (formatCondition.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlUniqueValues) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;类型为 xlUniqueValues&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;类型不为 xlUniqueValues&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
