    {
      "name": "ModifyAppliesToRange",
      "summary": "<p>该区域必须采用 A1 引用样式，并全部包含在 <strong>FormatConditions</strong> 集合的父工作表内。可包括区域操作符（冒号）、相交区域操作符（空格）或合并区域操作符（逗号）。也可以使用货币符号，但会被忽略。</p>\n<p>您也可以在区域的任意部分中使用局部定义名称，但该名称必须使用宏语言。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>设置此格式规则所应用于的单元格区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式所应用于的单元格区域，并设置该条件格式内部的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A7:A10&quot;</span>))\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式所应用于的单元格区域，并将该条件格式的特定文本的字体设置为加粗和倾斜。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2:A4&quot;</span>))\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Italic</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
