    {
      "name": "SetFirstPriority",
      "summary": "<p>当工作表中有多个条件格式规则时，如果之前未将此规则设置为优先级“1”，此方法将导致工作表上的所有其他现有规则的优先级都增加 1。</p>\n<p>将在工作表级别应用条件格式规则的优先级。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>将此条件格式规则的优先级值设置为“1”，以便在工作表上的所有其他规则之前计算此规则。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式的优先级值设置为“1”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 上区域 B1:B10 中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式的优先级设置为“1”，然后设置该区域上第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式所应用于的数字格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> formatConditions = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>\n    formatConditions.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n    formatConditions.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">NumberFormat</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;0.00&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetLastPriority",
      "summary": "<p>优先级的实际值将等于工作表上条件格式规则的总数。当工作表中有多个条件格式规则时，此方法将导致优先级值大于此规则的规则的优先级降低 1。</p>\n<p>将在工作表级别应用条件格式规则的优先级。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>为此条件格式规则设置求值顺序，以便在工作表上的所有其他规则之后计算此规则。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式的求值顺序，然后设置该区域中第二个（UniqueValues）条件格式的内部颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> formatConditions = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>\n    formatConditions.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetLastPriority</span>()\n    formatConditions.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 上区域 B1:B10 中第一个（UniqueValues）条件格式的求值顺序，并显示该条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> uniqueValues = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetLastPriority</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(uniqueValues.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
